What Questions Do Clients Usually Ask?
Is Embassy Legalization Mandatory for Lebanese Certificates?
Yes. Embassy approval is required before MOFA stamping.

Do You Need Original Certificates?
Yes. Authorities require original documents for final attestation.

Can Someone Else Submit the Documents?
Yes. You can authorize us to handle the full process.

Is MOFA Attestation Required in UAE?
Yes. Without a MOFA stamp, UAE departments will not accept the document.

Can someone else submit my document?
Yes. An authorization letter allows a service provider to process it on your behalf.